text:
Essential Plus is a convenient store in a quiet neighborhood. The staff is friendly too.

It has many items including KitKat Strawberry which I found much cheaper than most sold in larger supermarkets!

Many soft drinks are priced at $1 too.
Owner is very kind and inside decorations is good. Available Myanmar food and fridge fish and meat.
Great! Nice selections … Thai, Vietnam, Myanmar groceries items all have. Its at Block 2.

nice shop with everyday essentials...
also very nice staff... sometimes there's a boy shopkeeper who is very cute..
